cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.MM 

This paper deals with the problem of image retrieval, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also discusses the use of textual data and natural language processing techniques, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The proposed method involves machine learning and prediction, which is a common theme in machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper specifically focuses on multimodal image retrieval (MIR), which is a subfield of multimedia (cs.MM).
